=3 | Scotland\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Scottish Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Scottish League Cup|League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[UEFA|Europe]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]]||[[1995\u201396 Rangers F.C. season|1995\u201396]]||[[Scottish Football League Premier Division|Scottish Premier Division]]||28||14||4||3||3||1||7||1||42||19\n|-\n|[[1996\u201397 Rangers F.C. season|1996\u201397]]||Scottish Premier Division||26||13||1||0||4||3||3||1||34||17\n|-\n|[[1997\u201398 Rangers F.C. season|1997\u201398]]||Scottish Premier Division||20||3||3||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||5||0||28||3\n|-\n! colspan=3 | England\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[FA Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[EFL Cup|League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[UEFA|Europe]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Middlesbrough F.C.|Middlesbrough]]||[[1997\u201398 Middlesbrough F.C. season|1997\u201398]]||First Division||7||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||8||0\n|-\n|[[1998\u201399 Middlesbrough F.C. season|1998\u201399]]||[[Premier League]]||26||3||1||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||29||3\n|-\n|[[1999\u20132000 Middlesbrough F.C. season|1999\u20132000]]||Premier League||8||1||1||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||11||1\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]]||[[2000\u201301 Everton F.C. season|2000\u201301]]||Premier League||14||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||15||0\n|-\n|[[2001\u201302 Everton F.C. season|2001\u201302]]||Premier League||18||1||4||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||23||1\n|-\n|[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]||[[2001\u201302 Burnley F.C. season|2001\u201302]]||First Division||6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||6||0\n|-\n! colspan=3 | China PR\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Chinese FA Cup|FA Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Chinese Super League Cup|CSL Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Asian Football Confederation|Asia]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[Gansu Tianma F.C.|Gansu Tianma]]||2003||[[China League One]]||4||2